# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../developers.rst:149
msgid ""
"Essentially, we are switching to the ``libopenshot/build`` folder, then "
"running ``cmake ..`` on the parent folder. This finds dependencies and "
"creates all the needed Makefiles used to compile this library. Then ``make`` "
